## 1. Miniconda Kurulumu
```bash
wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -O ~/miniconda.sh
bash ~/miniconda.sh
source ~/.bashrc
conda --version

conda config --add channels conda-forge
conda config --add channels bioconda
conda config --set channel_priority strict

# Paket kurulumu
conda install sra-tools fastqc fastp star samtools subread
# MultiQC iÃ§in pip gerekebilir:
pip install multiqc
```

---

## 2. Veri Ä°ndirme (SRA)
```bash
# SRR dosyasÄ±nÄ± indir
prefetch SRRXXXXXXX

# FASTQ'ya dÃ¶nÃ¼ÅŸtÃ¼r
fasterq-dump SRRXXXXXXX --split-files -e 6 -O .
```

---

## 3. Kalite Kontrol (FastQC & MultiQC)
```bash
# Kalite analizi
fastqc *.fastq.gz

# RaporlarÄ± birleÅŸtir
multiqc ./
```

---

## 4. FASTQ Temizleme (fastp)
```bash
fastp --in1 forward.fastq.gz --in2 reverse.fastq.gz \
      --out1 clean_forward.fastq.gz --out2 clean_reverse.fastq.gz
```

---

## 5. Referans Genomu Ä°ndeksleme (STAR)
```bash
STAR --runMode genomeGenerate \
     --genomeDir ref/ \
     --genomeFastaFiles genome.fna \
     --sjdbGTFfile annotation.gtf \
     --runThreadN 12
```

---

## 6. Hizalama (STAR)
```bash
for sample in *_1.fastq.gz; do
    base=$(basename "$sample" _1.fastq.gz)
    STAR --genomeDir ref/ \
         --readFilesIn ${base}_1.fastq.gz ${base}_2.fastq.gz \
         --runThreadN 12 \
         --outFileNamePrefix mapped/${base}_ \
         --outSAMtype BAM SortedByCoordinate;
done
```

---

## 7. BAM DosyasÄ± YÃ¶netimi (samtools)
```bash
# Gerekirse birleÅŸtirme Ã¶rneÄŸi
samtools merge merged.bam file1.bam file2.bam

# Ä°ndeksleme
samtools index merged.bam
```

---

## 8. SayÄ±m Matrisi OluÅŸturma (featureCounts)
```bash
featureCounts -a annotation.gtf \
              -o count.out \
              -T 4 bams/*.bam
```

